rows.text: While doing a stunt in local Gilroy, Zeke has a massive wipeout on his board attempting a 540 McTwist. The sponsor replaces Zeke with Kojo. Kojo has this very weird idea that involves yellow paint and music. When Zeke sees this he demands that Luther should help him get back up on his feet. At the time of the stunt Zeke nails the 540 McTwist, the crowd cheers.

After Luther impresses everyone with his skills and he finds out Zeke was ordered to babysit him, he becomes totally disobedient and winds up getting into a rap battle with the best rapper in town, Master Nasty.
